data.title: All included in one price
data.meta_description: Book a holiday home and explore Drbak. With Landfolk you get a holiday beyond the ordinary surrounded by nature.  Utility costs included  Cleaning included  Insurance included
data.text:
Snrvillen

Discover the charm of Snrvillen, a perfect getaway with scenic landscapes and cozy holiday homes. Whether you're exploring nearby trails or simply relaxing, Snrvillen offers a memorable escape for families, couples, and friends.

Slettefjell

Discover the serene beauty of Slettefjell. Perfect for hiking enthusiasts and nature lovers, this destination offers breathtaking mountain views and tranquil surroundings. Enjoy a peaceful retreat with family or friends in one of our charming holiday homes.

Hgevarde

Hgevarde is a charming Norwegian village nestled in the heart of the stunning Hardanger region. Explore the picturesque fjords, hike through the lush forests, and immerse yourself in the tranquil, friendly atmosphere of this hidden gem. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or an adventure-filled getaway, Hgevarde offers a truly memorable holiday experience.

Tynset

Nestled in the heart of Norway, Tynset offers a blend of serene nature and cultural experiences. Whether you're hiking through lush forests or exploring local heritage sites, there's something for everyone.

Kongsvinger

Discover the charm of Kongsvinger, a town steeped in history and surrounded by lush greenery. Enjoy a stroll through the old fortress or unwind by the Glomma river. Perfect for families, couples, and friends looking for a peaceful getaway.

Etnedal

Discover the serene beauty of Etnedal, a perfect retreat nestled in the heart of Norway. Enjoy hiking trails, picturesque landscapes, and a peaceful ambiance that makes for a memorable escape.

Hnefoss

Nestled by the Begna River, Hnefoss offers a serene getaway with beautiful nature surrounds. Enjoy a visit to the impressive Hnefossen waterfall or explore nearby hiking trails for an active holiday.

Ustaoset

Nestled in the scenic mountains, Ustaoset is a perfect getaway for nature lovers. Enjoy skiing in the winter and hiking trails with breathtaking views in the summer.

Rendalen

Discover the serene beauty of Rendalen, where pristine lakes and lush forests invite you to unwind. Perfect for fishing, hiking, and reconnecting with nature, Rendalen offers a peaceful retreat for families, couples, and friends alike.

Hurdal

Nestled in the heart of Norway, Hurdal offers a peaceful escape with its beautiful lakes, lush forests, and charming village atmosphere. Whether you're into hiking, fishing, or simply unwinding in nature, Hurdal has something special for everyone.

Southeast Norway

Discover the charm of Southeast Norway with its stunning fjords, picturesque villages, and scenic hiking trails. Perfect for families, couples, and friends looking to enjoy nature's beauty and rich cultural experiences.

Kristiansand

Kristiansand is a charming coastal town in southern Norway, known for its picturesque harbor, beautiful beaches, and vibrant cultural scene. Explore the historic city center, visit the lively market, or take a stroll along the scenic waterfront. With its friendly locals and abundance of outdoor activities, Kristiansand is the perfect destination for a relaxing and memorable holiday.

Oslo

Discover the vibrant city of Oslo, where modern architecture and rich cultural heritage come together to create a truly unique travel experience. Explore the charming neighborhoods, stroll along the picturesque fjords, and immerse yourself in the city's lively arts and music scene. Whether you're seeking adventure or relaxation, Oslo has something to captivate every visitor.

Fidjeland

Discover the charming village of Fidjeland, a hidden gem nestled in the heart of the countryside. Explore the quaint streets, browse the local shops, and immerse yourself in the tranquil atmosphere. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a base to explore the surrounding natural wonders, Fidjeland offers a truly memorable holiday experience.

Bergen

Nestled between majestic fjords and towering mountains, Bergen is a charming Norwegian city that offers a unique blend of natural beauty and cultural richness. Explore the colorful wooden houses of the historic Bryggen district, wander through the bustling fish market, and take a scenic ride on the Flibanen funicular for breathtaking views of the city and its surroundings. Whether you're seeking outdoor adventures or a glimpse into Norway's rich heritage, Bergen is the perfect destination for an unforgettable holiday.

Hafjell

Discover the charming mountain town of Hafjell, where the fresh air and stunning natural beauty will captivate your senses. Explore the nearby hiking trails, bike through the lush forests, or simply relax and soak in the peaceful atmosphere. Hafjell is the perfect destination for a memorable holiday getaway.

Stavanger

Discover the charming city of Stavanger, nestled along the stunning fjords of Norway. Explore the historic old town, with its colorful wooden houses and quaint cobblestone streets. Venture out to nearby islands and hike through the breathtaking natural landscapes, or simply relax and soak in the serene atmosphere. Stavanger offers a perfect blend of culture, nature, and adventure for your next holiday.

yer

Explore the charming town of yer, nestled in the heart of Norway's stunning Gudbrandsdalen valley. Immerse yourself in the region's rich history and natural beauty, with opportunities to hike through lush forests, discover picturesque villages, and experience the warm hospitality of the local community.

lesund

Discover the charming coastal town of lesund, nestled among the fjords of western Norway. Explore the colorful Art Nouveau architecture, stroll along the picturesque harbor, and immerse yourself in the vibrant local culture. Venture out to nearby islands and enjoy the stunning natural beauty of this unique Norwegian destination.

Hemsedal

Discover the charming mountain town of Hemsedal, a picturesque destination nestled in the heart of Norway's stunning fjord region. Explore the breathtaking natural beauty, from the towering peaks to the serene lakes and rivers. Enjoy a wide range of outdoor activities, from hiking and skiing to fishing and cycling, all set against a backdrop of majestic landscapes. Immerse yourself in the local culture and savor the delicious Norwegian cuisine. Hemsedal is the perfect place to create unforgettable memories on your next holiday adventure.

Larvik

Discover the charming coastal town of Larvik, nestled along the picturesque Vestfold region of Norway. Explore the historic harbor, stroll through the lush parks, and enjoy the stunning views of the Skagerrak Strait. Larvik offers a perfect blend of natural beauty and small-town warmth, making it an ideal destination for your next Norwegian adventure.

Trysil

Discover the charming town of Trysil, nestled in the heart of Norway's stunning Hedmark region. Surrounded by majestic mountains and pristine forests, Trysil offers a wealth of outdoor adventures, from skiing and snowboarding in the winter to hiking and biking in the summer. Immerse yourself in the local culture and explore the quaint shops and cozy cafes that dot the town's picturesque streets.
